high_descs: Move to the sponge on the counter to the right.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Bring the sponge to the sink on the right.
Wet the sponge in the sink with water.
Take the cleaned sponge from the sink, turn around, bring the sponge to the tub.
Put the sponge in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge in the tub.

high_descs: Turn right and move to the counter to the right of the toilet and to the left of the sink.
Pick up the green sponge near the front edge of the counter.
Turn left and move towards and then face the sink.
Place the sponge in the sink, rinse it using the faucet, and then pick up the sponge.
Turn around and move to the end of the bathtub closest to the bathroom door.
Place the sponge in the center of the bathtub.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed sponge in the bathtub.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to the sponge on the counter top by the toilet.
Pick up the sponge from the counter.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn around and walk forward to the bath tub.
Put the sponge in the bath tub basin.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge in a bath tub.

high_descs: Turn right and go to the wall to the left of the sink and face it.
Pick up the green backed sponge.
Turn right and walk to the front of the sink and face it.
Put the sponge under the tap and turn the water on and then turn it back off and retrieve the sponge.
Turn right and walk to the tub facing it so you are looking down the length of it..
Put the sponge in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place a wet sponge in the tub.

high_descs: Turn around, walk to counter with the sponge
Pick up the sponge from the counter
Walk to the sink
Put the sponge in the sink, turn on the faucet, turn off the faucet, pick up the sponge
Turn around, walk to the tub
Put the sponge inside the tub
anns.task_desc: Soak the sponge in the sink, put the wet sponge in the tub.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the end of the counter, right next to the toilet.
Pick up the sponge on the counter.
Take a step right and walk in front of the sink.
Wash the sponge in the sink.
Turn around and walk to the bath tub.
Put the sponge in the bath tub.
anns.task_desc: Put a washed sponge in a bath tub.
